Barbecue Beef

None

1.5::lbs::ground beef
3::None::onions
1::None::bell pepper
1::cups::celery
1.5::cups::ketchup
0.5::tablespoons::brown sugar
0.5::cups::water
1::teaspoons::dry mustard
0.25::cups::vinegar
None::None::Salt
None::None::Pepper

Brown meat in big pot. Add vegetables and water. Bring to a boil, then lower heat and simmer for 1 hour 15 minutes, until celery is soft. Add ketchup, brown sugar, mustard, vinegar, salt, and pepper. Cook another 10 minutes. Serve on hamburger rolls.
